458
00:20:44,708 --> 00:20:46,833
♪ I SAID, OH NO ♪

459
00:20:46,916 --> 00:20:49,541
♪ TIME TIME,
TIME TIME TO ATTACK... ♪

460
00:20:49,625 --> 00:20:53,250
( song continues )

461
00:20:59,125 --> 00:21:01,375
- ( gunfire continues )

462
00:21:04,208 --> 00:21:06,500
- PLAYING SOLDIER'S TOUGH WORK,
ISN'T IT?

463
00:21:06,583 --> 00:21:08,125
AND MY SOLDIERS ARE BETTER.

464
00:21:08,208 --> 00:21:10,041
'CAUSE THEY'VE GOT
WAY MORE EXPERIENCE.

465
00:21:10,125 --> 00:21:12,458
- YOU'RE HAPPY.
NOT THE MOOD I'D EXPECT

466
00:21:12,541 --> 00:21:14,416
FROM A GUY UNDER ATTACK,
BOSS-MAN.

467
00:21:14,500 --> 00:21:17,000
- I AM HAPPY. I'VE ALWAYS DREAMT
OF FIGHTING THESE GUYS,

468
00:21:17,083 --> 00:21:19,875
OR THE GUYS BEFORE THEM,
TO BE MORE PRECISE.

469
00:21:19,958 --> 00:21:22,791
AFTER VIETNAM, THE S.R. BUILT
ONE HELL OF A REP HERE,

470
00:21:22,875 --> 00:21:25,666
FOR THOSE IN THE KNOW.
AND THEY BUILT IT WITH GRIT.

471
00:21:25,750 --> 00:21:27,708
IT'S SAID THE JAPANESE
RAN THE ARMS TRADE

472
00:21:27,791 --> 00:21:29,333
WITH PISTOLS
TUCKED IN THEIR PANTS.

473
00:21:29,416 --> 00:21:30,875
THESE ARE THE CHILDREN OF MEN

474
00:21:30,958 --> 00:21:32,791
WHO MADE AN EMPIRE
FROM THE UNDERWORLD.

475
00:21:32,875 --> 00:21:35,333
AND I'VE BEEN TOLD
THEY BETRAYED MY FATHER.

476
00:21:35,416 --> 00:21:37,125
OF COURSE I WANT TO FACE THEM.

477
00:21:37,208 --> 00:21:39,708
BUT THIS IS NO STRIKE,
HE'S JUST TESTING ME.

478
00:21:39,791 --> 00:21:41,916
COLONEL HINOKI NEEDS
TO STOP PLAYING

479
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:42,958
AND BRING ME A REAL FIGHT.

480
00:21:43,041 --> 00:21:44,375
- I'LL BE DAMNED.

481
00:21:44,458 --> 00:21:46,458
HOW'D YOU TURN OUT
LIKE THIS, KASPER?

482
00:21:46,541 --> 00:21:49,083
AND YOU USED TO BE SO CUTE
WHEN YOU WERE YOUNGER.

483
00:21:53,208 --> 00:21:55,166
- OH, NO,
LOOKS LIKE REINFORCEMENTS.

484
00:21:59,208 --> 00:22:00,541
WHATEVER.

485
00:22:00,625 --> 00:22:03,333
JUST MAKE SURE
YOU KILL 'EM ALL.

